Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:43.26,ED_SC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(100,100)}可那风儿 越吼越凶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:43.26,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(100,100)}吹け吹け（叫んで）
